title: X-Men Battle of the Atom (COMPLETE)
description:
"Battle of the Atom" was an ongoing 10-part comic book crossover storyline published by Marvel Comics that debuted in September 2013 and ran through multiple X-Men books.

The story involved the X-Men of the future traveling to present time in order to force the All-New X-Men to return to their rightful time, as their presence in the current timeline will result in disastrous consequences.

This Torrent includes:

. The Publication history of X-Men: Battle of the Atom (2013) 
. Variant covers (if available)
. In English and in CBR format
